Package wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.particle

Class ParticleShapeDefinition

java.lang.Object
wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.particle.ParticleShapeDefinition
All Implemented Interfaces:
Registerable
public class ParticleShapeDefinition
extends Object
implements Registerable
Represents a defined particle shape. Shape definitions may be defined in JSON files in the plugin's particles directory.
Author:
Parker Hawke - Choco
